JOTAN: Versatile Norse giants of Rifts Earth

Jotan are Norse giants from the folklore traditions that survived into
Rifts Earth.  Their intelligence is higher than most giant races and
their attribute profile is more balanced, making them more versatile
OCC candidates.

ATTRIBUTES (APPROXIMATE RANGES)
  IQ: 6-16   ME: 6-16   MA: 6-16   PS: 13-38 (Supernatural)
  PP: 6-16   PE: 16-32  PB: 2-12   Spd: 9-24

DAMAGE POOL
  SDC: 4d6 x10 (approx 40-240)

SPECIAL ABILITIES
  - Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance
  - Better IQ than typical giants; broader OCC access
  - Giant size melee advantage

PENALTIES
  - Giant size limitations (equipment, buildings)
  - D-Bee status in Coalition territory

OCC ELIGIBLE: Yes.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

